data.description: Your new home awaits you in Williamsport! You do not wanna miss this three bedroom, two bath split foyer which boasts a finished basement , perfect for entertaining.  New roof was installed in April, one less thing you will have to worry about! Its close proximity to I-81 is convenient for easy access to restaurants and shopping. The paved driveway, deck, and side door entrance are just a few perks this home has to offer. Schedule your tour today!
